"title": "4363: silver",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4363: silver",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A precious metal often surpassed in value only by gold. It had a variety of uses and by NT times was common in coinage.</p>\n<h2>Silver mined</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:1-Job28:4\">JOB 28:1–28:4</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Silver acquired through trade</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:22\">1KI 10:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:9\">JER 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:12\">EZK 27:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:12\">REV 18:11–18:12</a></p>\n<h2>Silver refined</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:10\">PSA 66:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:3\">PRO 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:21\">PRO 27:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:10\">ISA 48:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:20-Ezek22:22\">EZK 22:20–22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:9\">ZEC 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:3\">MAL 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>Silver worked by silversmiths</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:4\">PRO 25:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:24\">ACT 19:24</a></p>\n<h2>Possession of silver a sign of wealth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:2\">GEN 13:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:35\">GEN 24:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:18\">NUM 22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:13\">DEU 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:17\">DEU 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:8\">JOS 22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27\">2CH 32:27</a> <em>Hezekiah's riches</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:13-Job3:15\">JOB 3:13–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:16\">JOB 27:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:37\">PSA 105:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:8\">ECC 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:7\">ISA 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:17\">ISA 60:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a> <em>the adornments of unfaithful Jerusalem</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:4\">EZK 28:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:43\">DAN 11:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:8\">HOS 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:3\">ZEC 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:14\">ZEC 14:14</a></p>\n<h2>Silver given as offerings to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:1-Exod25:3\">EXO 25:1–25:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:5\">EXO 35:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:24\">EXO 35:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:84-Num7:85\">NUM 7:84–7:85</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:11\">2SA 8:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:11\">1CH 18:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:7\">1CH 29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:11\">EZR 1:1–1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:68-Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:68–2:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:13-Ezra7:16\">EZR 7:13–7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:24-Ezra8:30\">EZR 8:24–8:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:71-Neh7:72\">NEH 7:71–7:72</a></p>\n<h2>Silver in the tabernacle</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:17\">EXO 38:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:18-Exod26:25\">EXO 26:18–26:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:23-Exod36:30\">EXO 36:23–36:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:31-Exod26:32\">EXO 26:31–26:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:35-Exod36:36\">EXO 36:35–36:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:9-Exod27:11\">EXO 27:9–27:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:9-Exod38:12\">EXO 38:9–38:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:17\">EXO 27:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:18-Exod38:19\">EXO 38:18–38:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:25-Exod38:28\">EXO 38:25–38:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:2\">NUM 10:2</a></p>\n<h2>Silver in the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14\">1CH 22:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:1\">2CH 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:15\">1KI 15:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:18\">2CH 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:15\">2KI 25:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:19\">JER 52:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:14-1Chr28:17\">1CH 28:14–28:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:2-1Chr29:5\">1CH 29:2–29:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:14\">2CH 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:2\">DAN 5:2</a></p>\n<h2>Silver abundant in Jerusalem in Solomon's time</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:15\">2CH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:27\">2CH 9:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:21\">1KI 10:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:20</a></p>\n<h2>Silver as currency</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:28\">GEN 37:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:16\">GEN 20:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:15-Gen23:16\">GEN 23:15–23:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:19\">GEN 33:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:35\">GEN 42:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:32\">EXO 21:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:25\">EXO 38:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:15\">LEV 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:6\">LEV 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:16\">LEV 27:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:50\">NUM 3:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:16\">NUM 18:16</a> <em>the redemption of firstborn males</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:6\">DEU 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:28\">DEU 2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:22-Deut14:26\">DEU 14:22–14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:19\">DEU 22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:28-Deut22:29\">DEU 22:28–22:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:32\">JOS 24:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:4\">JDG 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:5\">JDG 16:5</a> <em>The rulers of the Philistines offer to pay Delilah for the secret of Samson's great strength</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:10\">JDG 17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:8\">1SA 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:11\">2SA 18:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:24\">2SA 24:24</a> <em>David buys Araunah's threshing-floor and oxen</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:29\">1KI 10:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:17\">2CH 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:24\">1KI 16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:39\">1KI 20:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25\">2KI 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:6\">1CH 19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:6\">2CH 25:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:21-Ezra7:22\">EZR 7:21–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:15\">NEH 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:9\">EST 3:9</a> <em>Haman promises to pay those who destroy the Jews</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:11\">JOB 42:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:23\">ISA 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:9-Jer32:10\">JER 32:9–32:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:44\">JER 32:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:1-Hos3:2\">HOS 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6\">AMO 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:5-Amos8:6\">AMO 8:5–8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:11\">ZEP 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:12-Zech11:13\">ZEC 11:12–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:9\">MAT 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:15\">MAT 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:3-Matt27:10\">MAT 27:3–27:10</a> <em>Judas returns the thirty silver coins</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:35\">LUK 10:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:6\">ACT 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Silver as tribute</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:33-2Kgs23:35\">2KI 23:33–23:35</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:3\">2CH 36:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18-1Kgs15:19\">1KI 15:18–15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2-2Chr16:3\">2CH 16:2–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:8\">2KI 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:14-2Kgs18:15\">2KI 18:14–18:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:13-2Chr9:14\">2CH 9:13–9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:23-2Chr9:24\">2CH 9:23–9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:11\">2CH 17:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr27:5\">2CH 27:5</a></p>\n<h2>Silver as plunder</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:19\">JDG 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:22\">EXO 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:21-Num31:23\">NUM 31:21–31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:18-Josh6:19\">JOS 6:18–6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:21\">JOS 7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:24\">2CH 25:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:13\">EZK 38:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:9\">NAM 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Silver idols or statues</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:23\">EXO 20:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25\">DEU 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:17\">DEU 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:1-Judg17:4\">JDG 17:1–17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:4\">PSA 115:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:20\">ISA 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:22\">ISA 30:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:7\">ISA 31:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:19\">ISA 40:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:6\">ISA 46:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:3-Jer10:4\">JER 10:3–10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:8-Jer10:9\">JER 10:8–10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:32\">DAN 2:32</a> <em>the statue in Nebuchadnezzar's dream</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:4\">DAN 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:4\">HOS 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:2\">HOS 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:19\">HAB 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:29\">ACT 17:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:24\">ACT 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20\">REV 9:20</a></p>\n<h2>Silver jewellery</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:53\">GEN 24:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:11\">SNG 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:17\">EZK 16:17</a></p>\n<h2>Silver referred to metaphorically</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:23-Job22:25\">JOB 22:23–22:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:6\">PSA 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:13\">PSA 68:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:72\">PSA 119:72</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:1-Prov2:5\">PRO 2:1–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:14\">PRO 3:13–3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:10\">PRO 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:19\">PRO 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:20\">PRO 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:16\">PRO 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:1\">PRO 22:1</a> <em>Esteem is better than silver or gold</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">PRO 25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:6\">ECC 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:22\">ISA 1:22</a></p>",
